fields.name: Life
fields.description: Stories about life, showcasing various aspects of human existence. These films depict struggles, successes, challenges, and joys that people encounter every day.

fields.name: Love
fields.description: Movies that touch the heart and soul, telling stories of true love and romantic adventures. From touching dramas to light-hearted comedies, everyone will find something close and moving.

fields.name: Battle
fields.description: Movies that narrate great battles and heroic fights. This category features epic tales of war, personal duels, and strategic confrontations

fields.name: Party
fields.description: Fun and dynamic movies filled with energy and celebrations. Here you will find comedies and dramas set against the backdrop of parties and social events.

fields.name: Mystery
fields.description: Thrilling movies that keep you on the edge of your seat until the very end. Mysteries, intrigues, and unexpected plot twists await you in this category.

fields.name: Adventure
fields.description: Stories of thrilling adventures and extraordinary journeys. These films take the viewer to new worlds full of dangers and discoveries.

fields.name: Journey
fields.description: Movies about the path and self-discovery, where characters embark on fascinating journeys. They discover new horizons and meet unexpected companions.

fields.name: Dream
fields.description: Movies that inspire and make you dream. They showcase worlds of fantasy and imagination, where anything is possible and every wish can come true.

fields.name: War
fields.description: Movies about war that depict its brutality and heroism. These stories narrate battles, strategies, and personal dramas set against the backdrop of military conflict.

fields.name: Hero
fields.description: Movies about heroes who overcome incredible obstacles to achieve their goals. These stories inspire feats and showcase the strength of the human spirit.
